<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="bb26Nov1938"><font color="red">26 November 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Richard de la Mere): I am sending you enclosed the new version of the last pages of the book &hellip; Reckon the corrections and additions on the galleys of Part III to be more or less equal to those which were made on those of Part I. Part II on the contrary will have much less corrections (except a little more on Episode IV). By the way the printers have initialled the galleys they sent &ldquo;End of Episode B&rdquo; &hellip; I had written &ldquo;End of episode III&rdquo;. </div>
